Package: libva-v4l2-stateful
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: VA-API driver for V4L2 stateful video decoders
 This package provides a VA-API backend driver that wraps V4L2 stateful
 (memory-to-memory) video decoders, enabling VA-API-only applications
 to use hardware video decode on platforms with V4L2-only interfaces.
 .
 Supported codecs: H.264, HEVC, VP8, VP9, AV1
 .
 Target hardware: CIX Sky1 VPU (Linlon Video device)
 .
 Enables hardware decode in:
  - Firefox (VA-API)
  - Chromium (VA-API)
  - mpv (--hwdec=vaapi-copy)
